        "Params": "{3: 'In the story, the Duke of Milan and his daughter Miranda were betrayed and stranded on a deserted island. Twelve years later, their enemy, the King of Naples, sails near the island, and the Duke asks the fairy to summon a tempest with magic to capsize their ship.'}"
    },
